---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/architecture.css';

const title = "ION Network · Architecture";
const description = "A reference architecture for the ION Network — governance, network profile, core services, and Beckn participant interactions.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} bodyClass={"architecture"}>
<header class="nav">
    <div class="wrap nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#top">
        <span class="brand-mark">I</span>
        <span>ION Network</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#diagram">Architecture</a>
        <a href="#tiers">Layers</a>
        <a href="#protocol">Protocol</a>
        <a href="/overview/transaction/">Transaction</a>
        <a href="/overview/transaction-with-payment/">Transaction + Payment</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top" class="wrap">

    <section class="hero">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>Reference architecture</span>
      <h1>An open commerce network, ratified by a council, run on Beckn.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        ION layers governance, a network profile, and three core services on top of the Beckn protocol —
        connecting buyer apps, providers, and consumers across Indonesian commerce.
      </p>
      <div class="meta">
        <span class="chip"><strong>5</strong> layers</span>
        <span class="chip"><strong>3</strong> core services</span>
        <span class="chip"><strong>BAP ↔ BPP</strong> interactions</span>
        <span class="chip">Beckn Protocol</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="cta primary" href="/overview/transaction/">Trade × Logistics walk-through <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a class="cta primary" href="/overview/transaction-with-payment/">Trade × Payment × Logistics walk-through <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a class="cta secondary" href="#diagram">Skip to architecture</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="diagram" class="diagram">
      <div class="diagram-card">
        <!-- Architecture diagram -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1240 920" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-labelledby="title desc">
          <title id="title">ION Network Architecture</title>
          <desc id="desc">Five-tier diagram: Council, Network profile, Core services, Participants, Consumer.</desc>

          <defs>
            <marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="var(--rail)"/>
            </marker>
            <marker id="arrowAccent" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="var(--accent)"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>

          <style>
            .tier-label { font: 600 11px "Inter", system-ui; fill: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 1.4px; text-transform: uppercase; }
            .box-title  { font: 600 17px "Inter", system-ui; fill: var(--ink); }
            .box-sub    { font: 400 13px "Inter", system-ui; fill: var(--text-2); }
            .box-detail { font: 400 13px "Inter", system-ui; fill: var(--text); }
            .edge-label { font: italic 12px "Inter", system-ui; fill: var(--muted); }
            .edge-label.accent { fill: var(--accent); }
            .pill        { font: 500 13px "Inter", system-ui; fill: var(--ink); }
          </style>

          <!-- Tier labels -->
          <text class="tier-label" x="40" y="60">L1 · Governance</text>
          <text class="tier-label" x="40" y="220">L2 · Network profile</text>
          <text class="tier-label" x="40" y="400">L3 · Core services</text>
          <text class="tier-label" x="40" y="600">L4 · Participants</text>
          <text class="tier-label" x="40" y="860">L5 · End user</text>

          <!-- L1: ION Council -->
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="490" y="76" width="260" height="78" rx="14" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <rect x="490" y="76" width="6" height="78" rx="3" fill="var(--accent)"/>
            <text class="box-title" x="620" y="110" text-anchor="middle">ION Council</text>
            <text class="box-sub"   x="620" y="132" text-anchor="middle">Governance body</text>
          </g>

          <!-- ratifies -->
          <line x1="620" y1="154" x2="620" y2="220" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowAccent)"/>
          <text class="edge-label accent" x="632" y="190">ratifies</text>

          <!-- L2: ION Network -->
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="350" y="232" width="540" height="116" rx="14" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <text class="box-title" x="620" y="262" text-anchor="middle">ION Network</text>
            <text class="box-sub"   x="620" y="284" text-anchor="middle"><tspan font-style="italic">ion.yaml</tspan> — network profile</text>
            <line x1="380" y1="298" x2="860" y2="298" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <!-- two pills -->
            <rect x="380" y="310" width="220" height="28" rx="8" fill="var(--panel-alt)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <text class="pill" x="490" y="328" text-anchor="middle">Policy Registry</text>
            <rect x="640" y="310" width="220" height="28" rx="8" fill="var(--panel-alt)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <text class="pill" x="750" y="328" text-anchor="middle">Error Registry</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Trunk -->
          <line x1="620" y1="348" x2="620" y2="380" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="180" y1="380" x2="1060" y2="380" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="180" y1="380" x2="180" y2="416" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
          <line x1="620" y1="380" x2="620" y2="416" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
          <line x1="1060" y1="380" x2="1060" y2="416" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>

          <!-- L3: Services -->
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="60" y="424" width="240" height="92" rx="14" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <text class="box-title" x="180" y="458" text-anchor="middle">ION Registry</text>
            <text class="box-sub"   x="180" y="482" text-anchor="middle" font-style="italic">on DeDi</text>
          </g>
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="500" y="424" width="240" height="92" rx="14" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <text class="box-title" x="620" y="458" text-anchor="middle">Catalogue Service</text>
            <text class="box-sub"   x="620" y="482" text-anchor="middle" font-style="italic">Beckn Fabric</text>
          </g>
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="940" y="424" width="240" height="92" rx="14" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <text class="box-title" x="1060" y="458" text-anchor="middle">Discover Service</text>
            <text class="box-sub"   x="1060" y="482" text-anchor="middle" font-style="italic">CDS</text>
          </g>

          <!-- service edge labels + connectors to participants -->
          <text class="edge-label" x="180" y="546" text-anchor="middle">registers</text>
          <text class="edge-label" x="620" y="546" text-anchor="middle">publishes</text>
          <text class="edge-label" x="1060" y="546" text-anchor="middle">queries · subscribes</text>

          <line x1="180"  y1="552" x2="180"  y2="612" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
          <line x1="620"  y1="552" x2="620"  y2="612" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
          <line x1="1060" y1="552" x2="1060" y2="612" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>

          <!-- L4: Participants -->
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="40" y="620" width="280" height="116" rx="14" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <rect x="40" y="620" width="6" height="116" rx="3" fill="var(--accent)"/>
            <text class="box-title" x="180" y="654" text-anchor="middle">BAP</text>
            <text class="box-sub"   x="180" y="678" text-anchor="middle">Buyer apps</text>
            <text class="box-detail" x="180" y="704" text-anchor="middle">Tokopedia · Shopee · Lazada</text>
          </g>
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="480" y="620" width="280" height="116" rx="14" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <rect x="480" y="620" width="6" height="116" rx="3" fill="var(--accent)"/>
            <text class="box-title" x="620" y="654" text-anchor="middle">BPP</text>
            <text class="box-sub"   x="620" y="678" text-anchor="middle">Provider platforms</text>
            <text class="box-detail" x="620" y="704" text-anchor="middle">Merchants · JNE · J&amp;T · LSPs</text>
          </g>
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="920" y="620" width="280" height="116" rx="14" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <rect x="920" y="620" width="6" height="116" rx="3" fill="var(--accent)"/>
            <text class="box-title" x="1060" y="654" text-anchor="middle">BAP</text>
            <text class="box-sub"   x="1060" y="678" text-anchor="middle">Additional buyer apps</text>
            <text class="box-detail" x="1060" y="704" text-anchor="middle">Partner storefronts · niche apps</text>
          </g>

          <!-- BAP <-> BPP arrows -->
          <line x1="320" y1="668" x2="478" y2="668" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowAccent)"/>
          <text class="edge-label accent" x="399" y="660" text-anchor="middle">/select</text>

          <line x1="478" y1="700" x2="320" y2="700" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrowAccent)"/>
          <text class="edge-label accent" x="399" y="722" text-anchor="middle">/on_select</text>

          <!-- Beckn Protocol Strip -->
          <g>
            <rect x="40" y="760" width="1160" height="64" rx="12" fill="var(--accent-2)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-opacity="0.4"/>
            <text x="620" y="788" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fraunces, Georgia, serif" font-weight="600" font-size="16" fill="var(--ink)">Beckn Protocol Exchange</text>
            <text x="620" y="810" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="13" fill="var(--text)">/init   ·   /confirm   ·   /status   ·   /track   ·   /update   ·   /reconcile</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Connector to Consumer -->
          <line x1="180" y1="824" x2="180" y2="868" stroke="var(--rail)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>

          <!-- L5: Consumer -->
          <g class="node">
            <rect class="body" x="60" y="868" width="240" height="44" rx="10" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--border)"/>
            <text x="180" y="896" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui" font-size="14">
              <tspan fill="var(--ink)" font-weight="600">Consumer</tspan>
              <tspan fill="var(--muted)" font-style="italic"> — uses the app</tspan>
            </text>
          </g>
        </svg>

        <div class="legend">
          <span class="item"><span class="swatch accent"></span> ION-governed flow</span>
          <span class="item"><span class="swatch"></span> Service relationship</span>
          <span class="item" style="margin-left:auto;color:var(--muted);">Hover any node to highlight.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="tiers" class="tiers">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>The five layers, top to bottom</h2>
        <span class="hint">Governance → Profile → Services → Participants → User</span>
      </div>

      <div class="tier-grid">
        <article class="tier span-4">
          <span class="tier-tag"><span class="bar"></span> L1 — Governance</span>
          <h3>ION Council</h3>
          <p>The ratifying body. Sets policies, approves changes to the network profile, and arbitrates disputes between participants.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="tier span-8">
          <span class="tier-tag"><span class="bar"></span> L2 — Network profile</span>
          <h3>ION Network &amp; registries</h3>
          <p><code>ion.yaml</code> defines the network. The Policy Registry encodes what's allowed; the Error Registry standardises how participants report failure.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>ion.yaml</li>
            <li>Policy Registry</li>
            <li>Error Registry</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="tier span-4">
          <span class="tier-tag"><span class="bar"></span> L3 — Service</span>
          <h3>ION Registry</h3>
          <p>The on-DeDi directory of every participant. BAPs and BPPs register here so the network knows who's authorised to transact.</p>
          <ul><li>on DeDi</li></ul>
        </article>

        <article class="tier span-4">
          <span class="tier-tag"><span class="bar"></span> L3 — Service</span>
          <h3>Catalogue Service</h3>
          <p>BPPs publish their offerings to the Beckn Fabric so buyer apps can search across providers without point-to-point integrations.</p>
          <ul><li>Beckn Fabric</li></ul>
        </article>

        <article class="tier span-4">
          <span class="tier-tag"><span class="bar"></span> L3 — Service</span>
          <h3>Discover Service (CDS)</h3>
          <p>BAPs query and subscribe to discover catalogues, providers, and updates relevant to their users.</p>
          <ul><li>queries</li><li>subscribes</li></ul>
        </article>

        <article class="tier span-6">
          <span class="tier-tag"><span class="bar"></span> L4 — Participant</span>
          <h3>BAP — Beckn Application Platform</h3>
          <p>The buyer-facing surface. Calls <code style="font-family:JetBrains Mono,monospace;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-2);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:5px;">/select</code> to express intent and consumes <code style="font-family:JetBrains Mono,monospace;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-2);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:5px;">/on_select</code> back from BPPs.</p>
          <ul><li>Tokopedia</li><li>Shopee</li><li>Lazada</li><li>Partner apps</li></ul>
        </article>

        <article class="tier span-6">
          <span class="tier-tag"><span class="bar"></span> L4 — Participant</span>
          <h3>BPP — Beckn Provider Platform</h3>
          <p>The supply-side surface. Merchants and logistics providers expose inventory, fulfilment, and order-state through standard endpoints.</p>
          <ul><li>Merchants</li><li>JNE</li><li>J&amp;T</li><li>LSPs</li><li>Warehouses</li></ul>
        </article>

        <article id="protocol" class="tier span-12" style="background:transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">
          <div class="protocol">
            <b>Beckn Protocol Exchange</b>
            <span style="color:var(--text-2);font-size:14px;">— shared rail between every BAP and BPP:</span>
            <span class="endpoints">
              <code>/init</code><code>/confirm</code><code>/status</code>
              <code>/track</code><code>/update</code><code>/reconcile</code>
            </span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="tier span-12">
          <span class="tier-tag"><span class="bar"></span> L5 — End user</span>
          <h3>Consumer</h3>
          <p>The person opening a buyer app. Everything above exists so a consumer in Jakarta can search a single storefront and transact with any registered provider on the network.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="attribution">
      <div class="attribution-card">
        <div class="text">
          <span class="label">Provided by</span>
          <span class="name">APINDO — Asosiasi Pengusaha Indonesia</span>
          <span class="desc">The Employers' Association of Indonesia, supporting open commerce infrastructure for Indonesian businesses.</span>
        </div>
        <a class="logo-link" href="https://apindo.or.id" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Visit APINDO">
          <img src="/apindo-logo.png" alt="APINDO" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <span>Created and managed by <a href="https://apindo.or.id" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apindo UMKM</a></span>
      <span><a href="#top">Back to top ↑</a></span>
    </footer>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
